<H3> <TI>   Federal Police Seeking `External' Funds For Operations in Amazon Region </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94WD0164B Brasilia CORREIO BRAZILIENSE in Portuguese 25 Dec 
93 p 5 </F>

<F P=103> 94WD0164B </F>
